<i>noun</i>: 돼지죽 [돼ː지죽] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>돼지죽 [돼ː지죽]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pigwash</dd><br>
<dd>죽처럼 만든 돼지의 먹이.</dd><br>
<dd>Pigs' feed made like porridge.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rubbish; unappetizing food</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 맛이나 상태가 매우 나쁜 음식.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) Food that has a terrible taste or is in an extremely bad condition.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>